/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會去六大賭場以外會係咩人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦<br />\n反正得啲廢老會去賭<br />\n我就想政府收返拆晒起公屋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(不過塊地咁靚冇咩可能)<br />\n<br />\n六大賭場之外嘅,10間有9間都係澳博<br />\n得啲細戶會去賭吓<br />\n入場費比大賭廳低唔少"},{"pid":"dd9dd864c0e38f89566d0ca7210bb1d35e60ecea","tid":1036712,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"我諗以前澳門想將賭業搞得多元化啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗賭場之外 仲有賽馬 賽狗 回力球 白鴿票等<br />\n但吸引力根本唔夠 影響賽果太著跡啲人覺得唔公道 漸漸收皮"},{"pid":"ca5f8db860d20db8c5d77f3618a3340b65d63194","tid":1036712,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227755fa381a85e311c84e38624929d31cfd671d","tid":1036712,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5705997f08630a0e16c4dc8c17a401d4b8584cc2","tid":1036712,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cafd6f60591636cb3085e61c9c7664f740bd74","tid":1036712,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"差政府好多錢(上億)<br />\n好似就嚟要還<br />\n依家想改變一部分土地用途<br />\n可能起賭場或者酒店<br />\n不過都差唔多收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"賽馬會啲賭會得副牌？<br />\n<br />\n勁殘咼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會去六大賭場以外會係咩人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦<br />\n反正得啲廢老會去賭<br />\n我就想政府收返拆晒起公屋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(不過塊地咁靚冇咩可能)<br />\n<br />\n六大賭場之外嘅,10間有9間都係澳博<br />\n得啲細戶會去賭吓<br />\n入場費比大賭廳低唔少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"其實六大入面澳博感覺都好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n人地氹仔間間賭場都搞到有聲有色<br />\n<br />\n發展好多非博彩元素（購物、飲食、娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係大賭客都有野玩<br />\n<br />\n同時令到賭場成件事少左烏烟瘴氣感覺<br />\n<br />\n但澳門半島個新葡京已經開始舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936f65be8b146228ad32b24e260a112021e88369","tid":1036712,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd9dd864c0e38f89566d0ca7210bb1d35e60ecea","tid":1036712,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"我諗以前澳門想將賭業搞得多元化啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗賭場之外 仲有賽馬 賽狗 回力球 白鴿票等<br />\n但吸引力根本唔夠 影響賽果太著跡啲人覺得唔公道 漸漸收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"白鴿票好耐就有<br />\n係澳門最早賭博之一<br />\n<br />\n澳門係19世紀後漸漸沒落<br />\n畀香港/廣州呢啲大港口取代左<br />\n當時窮到閪咁<br />\n只可以開賭<br />\n咁岩好有一段時間內地同香港係禁賭<br />\n結果澳門一嘢發達<br />\n集合晒黃賭毒(鴉片)<br />\n不過賭仲係中式賭博為主<br />\n<br />\n西式賭博出現<br />\n要到20世紀初<br />\n中式賭博開始沒落<br />\n澳葡政府就慢慢引入西式賭博<br />\n直到回歸後2006年開放賭權<br />\n澳博幾十年嚟係獨家,賺到笑"},{"pid":"b579746b72226b075561e122b18340abf0cf447e","tid":1036712,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca5f8db860d20db8c5d77f3618a3340b65d63194","tid":1036712,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227755fa381a85e311c84e38624929d31cfd671d","tid":1036712,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5705997f08630a0e16c4dc8c17a401d4b8584cc2","tid":1036712,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"賽馬會啲賭會得副牌？<br />\n<br />\n勁殘咼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會去六大賭場以外會係咩人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦<br />\n反正得啲廢老會去賭<br />\n我就想政府收返拆晒起公屋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class